TRENTON BOARD OF EDUCATION, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
TRENTON EDUCATION ASSOCIATION, Defendant-Respondent. C-961 September Term 2018
082573 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000262-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
